      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/namibian-oil-company-s-chief-is-cleared-of-fraud-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项独立调查宣判纳米比亚国家石油公司总经理无罪，他被控转移资金购买安哥拉石油区块。]]></description>
