    <item>
      <title>美国劳工数据和 30 年期债券拍卖前全球债券上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/global-bonds-gain-ahead-of-us-labor-data-30-year-bond-auction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者等待美国劳动力市场数据和美联储决策者的讲话以更清晰地了解货币政策路径，全球债券上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/global-bonds-gain-ahead-of-us-labor-data-30-year-bond-auction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 09:23:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莱茵金属首席执行官称，军火热潮是他所见过的最大规模</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rheinmetall-ceo-says-arms-boom-is-the-biggest-he-s-ever-seen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧洲为应对俄罗斯入侵乌克兰而加强防御，莱茵金属股份公司实现了创纪录的增长，预计未来几年其年度收入将大幅增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rheinmetall-ceo-says-arms-boom-is-the-biggest-he-s-ever-seen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 09:09:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称韦丹塔将暂停出售价值 25 亿美元的钢铁业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/vedanta-is-said-to-put-2-5-billion-steel-business-sale-on-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，韦丹塔有限公司 (Vedanta Ltd.) 已暂停出售其钢铁业务的计划，因为 10 亿美元的股票出售为该公司的财务带来了更多的喘息空间，而且环境和监管问题阻碍了潜在的竞标者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/vedanta-is-said-to-put-2-5-billion-steel-business-sale-on-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 09:03:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其排除提前降息的可能性，继续关注月度价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/turkish-central-bank-keeps-year-end-inflation-outlook-unchanged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行表示，将维持货币政策紧缩，直至月度通胀率永久放缓，并强调其致力于避免过早降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/turkish-central-bank-keeps-year-end-inflation-outlook-unchanged</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 07:55:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利通胀加速，降息空间缩小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/hungary-inflation-accelerates-narrowing-room-for-more-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利通胀率小幅上升，突破了央行容忍区间的上限，缩小了持续一年多的货币宽松周期的延续空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/hungary-inflation-accelerates-narrowing-room-for-more-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行敦促印度银行在危机中寻找增加存款的方法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rbi-says-banks-need-to-use-branches-to-draw-deposits-amid-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行行长表示，印度银行应该研究各种方法来吸引更多家庭储蓄，因为越来越多的人将资金投入投资产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rbi-says-banks-need-to-use-branches-to-draw-deposits-amid-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 05:55:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
